00:00:34.945 --> 00:00:37.079
Yeah, I work on our mentorship programs to help

00:00:37.079 --> 00:00:39.509
support student learning and improve their experience.

00:00:39.509 --> 00:00:40.854
That's really amazing, Miriam.

00:00:40.854 --> 00:00:42.459
You do so much for the student community,

00:00:42.460 --> 00:00:43.905
and I know they really appreciate it.

00:00:43.905 --> 00:00:46.679
