00:00:54.390 --> 00:00:55.980
Thank you so much.

00:00:55.979 --> 00:00:57.479
So, I was wondering,

00:00:57.479 --> 00:00:58.949
my mom's birthday is coming up.

00:00:58.950 --> 00:01:00.800
Would you mind making a cake for her?

00:01:00.799 --> 00:01:02.299
Oh my gosh. I would be honored.

00:01:02.299 --> 00:01:04.075
That's awesome. Thanks so much, Miriam.

00:01:04.075 --> 00:01:05.260
