00:01:19.454 --> 00:01:22.829
jQuery because this new tool is provided right in the browser.

00:01:22.829 --> 00:01:25.125
So, what is this life-changing tech?

00:01:25.125 --> 00:01:27.219
Drum roll please.

00:01:27.219 --> 00:01:30.650
I give you the Fetch API.

00:01:30.650 --> 00:01:33.034
So, yeah, the name isn't all that impressive-sounding,

00:01:33.034 --> 00:01:35.660
